&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Appropriate Levels&lt;/strong&gt; - Right number of approval levels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clear Criteria&lt;/strong&gt; - Well-defined approval criteria&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reasonable Timeouts&lt;/strong&gt; - Appropriate response time requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Backup Approvers&lt;/strong&gt; - Delegate and substitute approver setup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Audit Compliance&lt;/strong&gt; - Maintain complete approval audit trails&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Performance Optimization Best Practices&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;performance-optimization-best-practices&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
